Package: hansensherring
Type: Package
Title: Displaying 0-group herring data over a map of the northern Barent's Sea
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Trym", "Hansen Skarshaug",
      email = "trska2186@uib.no",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Displays trawl station as points on a map.
  Each station displays individuals caught, mean weight, mean length, 
    histograms showing weight (g) and length (mm).
